                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Moffat</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Extract—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-12-31">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 31, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Moffat reports the unanimous election of Estrada and Diaz as president and
                    vice president respectively. He says there is intense enthusiasm.</p>
                <postscript>
                    <p>[To be continued in <ref target="frus1911">Foreign Relations,
                        1911</ref>.]</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
